div.p:
Some of vs do gladly preach the word, we willingly declare good tidings and publiſh ſalvation, ſaying vnto you, your God reigneth;
                  Eſai. 52.7. yet hereby are we not iuſtified: our evill enſample may make the name of God to be blasphemed among the people;
                  Rom. 2.24. & if wee beate not downe our bodies and bring them into ſubiection, it may be that after we haue preached to others, our ſelues may prooue caſtavvaies. It is Saint Paules iudgement, 1. Cor. 9.27.
